data.description: Discover your dream home in the exclusive Rancho Murieta South community! Protected by a security gate guard, this haven boasts mature, low-maintenance landscaping. A charming back patio overlooking the serene fairway of the 7th hole of the golf course. Step inside to find a welcoming open floor plan with neutral colors, architectural details, and abundant natural light. The high ceilings add a touch of grandeur, while the main-level living ensures convenience. The master bedroom offers a slider to the backyard oasis and a luxurious soaking tub in the en-suite bath. With a 3-car garage and the option to convert the office into a 4th bedroom, this property has it all. Don't miss your chance to call this home!
